 assessed and dealt with, such that it does not pose a unacceptable risk to ground or surface water.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10762192  In accordance with Paragraph 109 and 121 of the NPPF.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
